{"tid":1870161,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"王陽翎 全解疫症亂局：港府搶購口罩受挫敗之謎、 不全數封關有更多原因、 醫護罷工令人敬重、 港14天居家檢疫遠遜新加坡","createTime":"2020-02-08T15:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T15:42:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9525bd9245b408f9a23afd7326b2f7252b2dbb15","tid":1870161,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"王陽翎<br />\n全解疫症亂局：港府搶購口罩受挫敗之謎、<br />\n不全數封關有更多原因、<br />\n醫護罷工令人敬重、<br />\n港14天居家檢疫遠遜新加坡<br />\n《政解專輯．悶透社．王陽翎（于非）》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n悶透社gumboringer<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020年踏入2月，中國、香港、澳門乃至全球均面臨新型病毒肺炎疫症危機，到底關於「口罩缺乏、不封關、14日家中檢疫、醫護工會罷工」應如何確切理解？<br />\n<br />\n【參考連結】<br />\n<br />\n1）【武漢肺炎】哈佛專家料1個月後達高峯 籲勿赴香港等「第二層感染地區」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/intern...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fintern...&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=9ccfc4fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fintern...&h=f138e740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/intern...</a><br />\n<br />\n2）醫管局口罩存貨能用多約一個月 承認採購裝備有困難<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/醫管局口罩存貨能用多約...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%AD%98%E8%B2%A8%E8%83%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%9A%E7%B4%84...&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=05d17aee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/醫管局口罩存貨能用多約...</a><br />\n<br />\n3）【醫護罷工】延長罷工有分歧 內科護士：能達目的也要試 年輕護士：怕被釘牌擬下周一復工<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/artic...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Fartic...&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=9a4bd6ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Fartic...&h=d16b5ccd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h